<h2>Change in bowel habits and Worms in stool</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms change in bowel habits and worms in stool including Pinworms, Ascaris worms, and Irritable bowel syndrome.</p>
<p>There  are 7 conditions  associated with change in bowel habits and worms in stool. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
</div>
<div class="related_conditions">
<ul class="results_list">
<li class="bg"><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e7bb4&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=274&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Pinworms</a><p>Pinworms are small worms that infect the intestines and cause intense itching around the anus.</p>
</li>
<li><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e8203&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=274&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Ascaris worms</a><p>Ascarisis is an infection by a roundworm, and can cause visible worms in the stool and respiratory symptoms.</p>
</li>
<li class="bg"><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e8078&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=274&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Irritable bowel syndrome</a><p>Irritable bowel syndrome is a common condition that causes painful spasms and cramping in the large intestine.</p>
</li>
<li><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e7ba6&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=274&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Gastroenteritis</a><p>Gastroenteritis is inflammation of the stomach and intestine that causes diarrhea and vomiting.</p>
</li>
<li class="bg"><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e7abe&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=274&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Dietary changes</a><p>Symptoms of dietary changes vary depending on the problem, they include constipation, diarrhea, and more.</p>
</li>
<li><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e81ac&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=274&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Colon polyps</a><p>Colon polyps are growths that form in the lining of the colon, and can cause constipation, diarrhea and more.</p>
</li>
<li class="bg"><a href="http://symptoms.webmd.com/coresc/landing?condition=091e9c5e808e80fa&amp;bpid[0]=24&amp;sid[0]=274&amp;bpid[1]=24&amp;sid[1]=451" onclick="return sl(this, '', 'sc-symindex-cmb_1');">Colon cancer</a><p>Colon cancer is often asymptomatic, but it can cause constipation, bowel obstruction, bloody stool and more.</p>
